lmów („Eraserhead”, „Elephant Man”, „Blue Velvet”), Lynch na zawsze wstrząsnął światem telewizji swoim serialem „Twin Peaks”, zanim zajął się kłamstwami Hollywood w „Mulholland Drive”. Śledząc życie najbardziej wpływowego filmowca swojego pokolenia, ten dokument bada ukryte znaczenie nieustannie spójnej filmografii i zagłębia się pod mroczną, rojącą się powierzchnię amerykańskiego snu.","popularity":0.4326,"poster_path":"/yHhwedBERAg0E7MQ5DutRNRoeIe.jpg","release_date":"2025-05-14","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":6.5,"vote_count":4},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/dJHpHNEOeGQ5eijyhYb6UtGRAPp.jpg","genre_ids":[28],"id":1391637,"title":"Jai Opetaia vs. David Nyika","original_language":"en","original_title":"Jai Opetaia vs. David Nyika","overview":"","popularity":0.056,"poster_path":"/9iNA6S14Hz7nnVXlQ3UFEtA7zpC.jpg","release_date":"2025-01-08","softcore":false,"video":true,"vote_average":0.0,"vote_count":0},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/K1qsqdgbAAfZpgc26SodTDdaCu.jpg","genre_ids":[28],"id":1529869,"title":"Liam Paro vs. David Papot","original_language":"en","original_title":"Liam Paro vs. David Papot","overview":"","popularity":0.0143,"poster_path":"/rxPIfXtiqmL6P42lZCJIVEVocDr.jpg","release_date":"2025-09-18","softcore":false,"video":true,"vote_average":0.0,"vote_count":0},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/h8JJ6xJCdhMNL6yYOuXpcJymB8p.jpg","genre_ids":[53,18],"id":1484003,"title":"DAVID'S LAW","original_language":"en","original_title":"DAVID'S LAW","overview":"","popularity":0.0454,"poster_path":"/s4EbZgWDZjkINGUaOHN4WV7X1SZ.jpg","release_date":"2025-04-06","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":10.0,"vote_count":1},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/agPXRs2GhiHlpP5DVrtQ0iG5EGR.jpg","genre_ids":[28],"id":1525049,"title":"David Allen vs. Arslanbek Makhmudov","original_language":"en","original_title":"David Allen vs. Arslanbek Makhmudov","overview":"","popularity":0.0566,"poster_path":"/ccWnUoAwwlVHYlu22xVvmPTFJJZ.jpg","release_date":"2025-10-11","